## 0 构建CMakeLists.txt文件&#13;
- 先声明 cmake 版本及项目名称&#13;
- 查找OpenCV包&#13;
``` CMakeLists.txt&#13;
find_package(OpenCV REQUIRED)&#13;
```&#13;
- 包含OpenCV头文件&#13;
```&#13;
include_directories(${OpenCV_INCLUDE_DIRS})&#13;
```&#13;
- 添加可执行文件&#13;
- 链接OpenCV库&#13;
```&#13;
target_link_libraries(ImageToGray ${OpenCV_LIBS})&#13;
```&#13;
